# Database & RLS

- Neon Postgres via Hyperdrive; Drizzle ORM only — no raw SQL in route handlers
- Every app table: `owner_id`, `enableRLS()`, `crudPolicy` / `pgPolicy` for `authenticated`
- Map Better Auth session user id to `auth.user_id()`; prove isolation in `test:rls`
- Pool Hyperdrive connections; never open a new client per request
- Cascade delete notes/reminders with applications; documents `application_id` SET NULL
